## 🔧 상세 설치

### Windows

```bash
# 1. FreeLang 설치 (https://freelang.dclub.kr/download/windows)
# 2. 프로젝트 클론
git clone https://gogs.dclub.kr/kim/freelang-v4-enterprise-platform.git

# 3. 실행
cd freelang-v4-enterprise-platform
freelang src/main.fl
```

### macOS

```bash
brew install freelang
git clone https://gogs.dclub.kr/kim/freelang-v4-enterprise-platform.git
cd freelang-v4-enterprise-platform
freelang src/main.fl
```

### Linux (Ubuntu/Debian)

```bash
sudo apt-get install freelang
git clone https://gogs.dclub.kr/kim/freelang-v4-enterprise-platform.git
cd freelang-v4-enterprise-platform
freelang src/main.fl
```

