## 📡 API 테스트

### 브라우저

```
http://localhost:3000/health
```

### cURL

```bash
# SaaS - 구독 생성
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/saas/subscribe \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"userId": 1, "planId": "starter"}'

# 금융 - 계좌 개설
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/finance/account \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"userId": 1, "initialCash": 10000}'

# 실시간 - 채널 구독
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/realtime/subscribe \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"userId": 1, "channel": "price_alerts"}'

# IoT - 디바이스 등록
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/iot/device \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"deviceId": "device_001", "name": "온실", "location": "서울"}'

# 엔터프라이즈 - 테넌트 생성
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/enterprise/tenant \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"name": "My Company"}'
```

