## 🚀 배포

### Docker

```dockerfile
FROM freelang:latest

WORKDIR /app
COPY . .

EXPOSE 3000
CMD ["freelang", "src/main.fl"]
```

```bash
docker build -t enterprise-platform .
docker run -p 3000:3000 enterprise-platform
```

### AWS Lambda / Serverless

```bash
# src/main.fl을 serverless handler로 변환 (향후)
freelang-serverless deploy
```

